Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Institutional Financial Svcs
Sub-Industry: Institutional Brokerage
Lampert Capital Markets, Inc. operates as an investment banking firm that provides financial advisory services. The Company offers strategic planning, consolidations, reorganization, mergers and acquisitions advisory, capital raising, fairness opinions, and valuation services. Lampert Capital Markets serves clients in the United States.




