Lampert Capital Markets Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 5:31 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Lampert Capital Markets Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Lampert Capital Markets Inc. is a boutique investment banking firm that offers financial advisory services. The firm provides private placements, initial and secondary public offerings, debt placements and restructurings, capital raising, and mergers and acquisitions advisory services. Additionally, it offers institutional sales and trading, securities brokerage, and pre-trade analysis services. The firm also provides cash management and corporate equity compensation planning and administration services. Lampert Capital Markets Inc. was formerly known as ICM Capital Markets Ltd. and changed its name to Lampert Capital Markets Inc. in February 2013. The firm is headquartered in New York, New ...
Lampert Capital Markets Inc. is a boutique investment banking firm that offers financial advisory services. The firm provides private placements, initial and secondary public offerings, debt placements and restructurings, capital raising, and mergers and acquisitions advisory services. Additionally, it offers institutional sales and trading, securities brokerage, and pre-trade analysis services. The firm also provides cash management and corporate equity compensation planning and administration services. Lampert Capital Markets Inc. was formerly known as ICM Capital Markets Ltd. and changed its name to Lampert Capital Markets Inc. in February 2013. The firm is headquartered in New York, New York with an additional office in Boca Raton, Florida. Lampert Capital Markets Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Lampert Debt Advisors.
