Lampert Capital Markets is in the business of buying and selling securities such as stocks, bonds, mutual funds and other investment-related products. This broker is registered with the SEC (#52234) and can engage in securities transactions on behalf of its customers (as a broker) or for its own account (as a dealer). Registered with 51 U.S. states and territoriesMission Statement: "Lampert Capital Markets is dedicated to providing its clients with unbiased advice and counsel to assist them in achieving their financial and investment objectives."
Firm data current as of 12/31/2015




